data.description: Within a charming neighborhood, this property is ideally situated in a delightful area, offering convenient proximity to downtown and various amenities. It is located adjacent to the picturesque Mills Park, a hub of community activity and frequent events.    Step inside this spacious home boasting 2067 square feet of living space. With 3 bedrooms and 2.5 bathrooms, this residence offers ample room for comfortable living. The layout is thoughtfully designed, emphasizing both functionality and style. Central air was installed July 2023. 2 car garage is attached.   The kitchen features Formica Countertops updated within the past year and has a convenient galley layout. A breakfast nook adds a cozy touch, perfect for morning gatherings. For formal occasions, the dedicated dining room provides an elegant space. The living room is an inviting retreat, complete with a wood-burning fireplace that creates a warm and inviting ambiance. The high ceilings amplify the sense of openness and airiness. Additionally, a supersize family room offers flexibility and room for relaxation and entertaining. Pool Table & Bar convey with the property, microwave, does not. Laminate flooring throughout except the bedrooms are carpeted.   Beyond the interiors, the exterior of this property is equally impressive. The large lot is graced with desert landscaping, ensuring easy maintenance while maintaining an attractive aesthetic.  Situated on a peaceful street, the property offers a serene atmosphere. Positioned directly across from Mills Park which is a hub of recreational activity, offering amenities such as volleyball courts, swimming facilities, skating areas, and peaceful picnic spots. The community center nearby adds to the convenience and sense of community.
